00:12:16.400 --> 00:12:20.680 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ben artık Albert Windsor değilim.

132
00:12:20.760 --> 00:12:24.600 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
O şahıs ağabeyi tahttan çekildiğinde

133
00:12:26.120 --> 00:12:27.440 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
onun tarafından öldürüldü.

134
00:12:27.520 --> 00:12:29.760 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Elbette Albert Windsor

135
00:12:29.840 --> 00:12:33.120 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
eski dostu Winston Churchill'e
şöyle demeyi çok isterdi.

136
00:12:33.720 --> 00:12:35.280 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
"Biraz geri çekil."

137
00:12:35.840 --> 00:12:39.760 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
