Ülkenin çıkarları mı yoksa
Anthony Eden'ın çıkarları mı?

145
00:13:22.800 --> 00:13:25.400 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Sizi buraya davet etmemin nedeni

146
00:13:26.440 --> 00:13:28.960 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Bay Churchill'den şikâyetlerini
dinlemek değil

147
00:13:29.040 --> 00:13:30.560 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
kendiminkileri size aktarmaktı.

148
00:13:31.920 --> 00:13:32.720 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Efendim?

149
00:13:34.480 --> 00:13:36.880 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Başbakan zamanı gelince çekilecek.

150
00:13:38.280 --> 00:13:41.120 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
O zamana kadar, hükümdar olarak

151
00:13:41.200 --> 00:13:47.080 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
danışılmaya, cesaretlendirmeye
ve uyarmaya hakkım var.

152
00:13:48.120 --> 00:13:53.120 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Sabırlı olup istediğini doğru zamanda

153
00:13:53.200 --> 00:13:54.720 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
elde etmek

154
00:13:56.040 --> 00:14:00.120 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
henüz hazır değilken bu makama geçmek
zorunda kalmaktan daha iyidir.

155
00:14:02.200 --> 00:14:04.240 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Kişisel tecrübelerimden konuşuyorum.

156
00:14:07.280 --> 00:14:08.600 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Dışişleri Bakanı.

157
00:14:09.600 --> 00:14:11.600 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Majesteleri.
-Efendim.

158
00:14:20.360 --> 00:14:21.800 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Dönüş yürüyüşüne başlayalım mı efendim?

159
00:14:52.440 --> 00:14:55.840 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Gaza basarsanız bir şey olmaz.
Teşekkürler.

160
00:14:55.920 --> 00:14:57.600 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Buradan yürüyecek miyiz?
-Philip.

161
00:14:57.680 --> 00:15:00.320 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Öyle görünüyor efendim.
-Teşekkürler.

162
00:15:00.400 --> 00:15:02.120 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Prenses Hazretleri.
-Teşekkürler.

163
00:15:03.280 --> 00:15:05.360 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Ben rehberinizim.
Sizi Treetops'a götüreceğim.

164
00:15:05.440 --> 00:15:10.720 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Harika, teşekkürler. Tüfeğimi verin.
Teşekkürler. Fişekleri de.

165
00:15:16.000 --> 00:15:19.680 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Buradan itibaren tamamen
sessiz olmanızı rica edeceğim.

166
00:15:19.760 --> 00:15:23.760 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Gerekli olmadıkça konuşmayın,
gerekirse sessizce konuşun.

167
00:15:23.840 --> 00:15:26.240 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Yolda bazı el işaretleri
kullanmamız gerekebilir.

168
00:15:26.800 --> 00:15:28.920 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Bu durun, bu da hareket etmeyin demektir.

169
00:15:29.000 --> 00:15:32.600 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Küçük gruplar olarak tek sıra hâlinde
gideceğiz. En fazla üç kişilik.

170
00:15:32.680 --> 00:15:35.520 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Bir şey yok, sıkıntı olmayacak.
Önden buyur.

171
00:15:35.600 --> 00:15:37.760 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Lütfen kol mesafesinde durun.

172
00:15:55.040 --> 00:15:58.800 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Tembo!</i>

173
00:15:58.880 --> 00:15:59.920 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Beyaz bayrak.

174
00:16:02.560 --> 00:16:03.560 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Gidin!

175
00:16:17.760 --> 00:16:20.320 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Şuna bir bak.

176
00:16:23.880 --> 00:16:25.120 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Yavaşça arkamdan yürüyün.

177
00:16:27.960 --> 00:16:30.160 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Size merdiveni indirecekler,
ben onu oyalarım.

178
00:16:30.240 --> 00:16:32.920 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Hayır. Sen Prenses ile kal.

179
00:16:33.000 --> 00:16:34.360 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Philip!
-Elizabeth, git.

180
00:16:34.440 --> 00:16:35.520 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Git.

181
00:16:35.600 --> 00:16:38.440 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Yakın durun Prenses Hazretleri.
Ceketime tutunun.

182
00:16:47.480 --> 00:16:49.400 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Bir şey yok Elizabeth.

183
00:16:49.480 --> 00:16:51.480 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Sakin ol!

184
00:16:53.600 --> 00:16:55.840 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Buradayım!

185
00:16:55.920 --> 00:16:57.720 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
İşte buradayım.

186
00:16:59.120 --> 00:17:01.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Yavaş olun Prenses Hazretleri.

187
00:17:09.319 --> 00:17:10.839 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Sakin ol. Bana odaklan.

188
00:17:10.920 --> 00:17:12.680 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Devam edin
Prenses Hazretleri. Çabuk!

189
00:17:13.720 --> 00:17:14.839 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Bana bak.

190
00:17:15.480 --> 00:17:17.119 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Uzaklaş!

191
00:17:20.400 --> 00:17:24.359 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Geri çekil. Git bakalım.

192
00:17:25.079 --> 00:17:26.760 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Sakince.

193
00:17:28.720 --> 00:17:30.040 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Kral sensin.

194
00:17:33.200 --> 00:17:34.200 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Aferin oğluma.

195
00:17:38.600 --> 00:17:40.360 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Tanrım.

196
00:17:46.680 --> 00:17:47.840 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Kusura bakma.
-Efendim.

197
00:17:48.480 --> 00:17:49.840 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Bunu nasıl yaptın?

198
00:17:52.520 --> 00:17:54.880 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Aptalın tekisin.
-Öyleyim.

199
00:17:58.240 --> 00:17:59.240 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Teşekkür ederim.

200
00:18:03.360 --> 00:18:04.200 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Düşünüyordum da...</i>

201
00:18:09.280 --> 00:18:11.760 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Babamın durumu iyiye giderse

202
00:18:12.840 --> 00:18:15.800 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Malta'ya dönebilir miyiz diye sorabilirim.

203
00:18:16.440 --> 00:18:19.680 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Sen de Donanma kariyerine devam edersin.
-Gerçekten mi?

204
00:18:23.280 --> 00:18:25.680 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Oradaki hayatımızı özlediğini biliyorum.

205
00:18:26.920 --> 00:18:27.920 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Özledim.

206
00:18:29.640 --> 00:18:31.200 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ben de özledim.

207
00:18:32.080 --> 00:18:33.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Hem de çok.

208
00:18:37.840 --> 00:18:39.200 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Babama yazacağım.

209
00:18:49.960 --> 00:18:51.920 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Hayır.
-Evet.

210
00:18:52.000 --> 00:18:53.480 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Kesinlikle olmaz.
-Kesinlikle olur.

211
00:18:53.560 --> 00:18:55.200 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Hayır!
-Haydi! Sadece bir kez!

212
00:18:55.280 --> 00:18:57.400 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Haydi öylesine bir tane!
-Bir tane ile bitmiyor!

213
00:18:57.480 --> 00:19:00.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Biter.
-Hayır!

214
00:19:00.240 --> 00:19:02.560 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Tembo.</i>

215
00:19:40.360 --> 00:19:41.520 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Teşekkürler.

216
00:19:42.720 --> 00:19:43.800 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Teşekkürler.

217
00:19:43.880 --> 00:19:45.040 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Karibu.</i>

218
00:19:49.280 --> 00:19:52.400 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Burada olmayan söylesin!

219
00:19:56.000 --> 00:19:57.800 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Pekâlâ.
-Günaydın beyler. Buyurun.

220
00:19:57.880 --> 00:20:03.920 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Bugün sekiz grup olacak.
Sağdan ikişerli ayrılıyoruz.

221
00:20:05.120 --> 00:20:07.200 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Araba başına.

222
00:20:07.280 --> 00:20:10.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Yani birinci de olsanız sekizinci de

223
00:20:10.080 --> 00:20:13.720 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
endişelenmenize gerek yok.
Size de pay düşecek.

224
00:20:16.600 --> 00:20:21.120 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
İki kısa boru sesi avın bittiği
anlamına gelir.

225
00:20:24.520 --> 00:20:27.440 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Hazır olunca araçlara geçin.
Çok teşekkürler.

226
00:20:30.800 --> 00:20:33.120 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Merhaba.
-Bir kişilik yer var mı?

227
00:20:33.680 --> 00:20:34.880 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Her zaman.

228
00:20:38.600 --> 00:20:40.840 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Peki o zaman.
-Debriyaja dikkat et.

229
00:20:40.920 --> 00:20:43.360 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Gözlerin yolda olsun. Çok hızlı gitme.

230
00:20:43.440 --> 00:20:45.720 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Merak etme.
Sana nazik davranacağım baba.

231
00:22:12.320 --> 00:22:13.760 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Bravo!

232
00:22:21.720 --> 00:22:24.720 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>Kalabalığın sevinci Kral'ın aracının</i>
<i>geldiği haberini verdi.</i>

233
00:22:24.800 --> 00:22:28.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>Majesteleri ve Prenses Margaret</i>
<i>havaalanına gelip</i>

234
00:22:28.080 --> 00:22:30.800 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Kraliyet yolcularına veda etti.</i>

235
00:22:30.880 --> 00:22:34.920 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>Prenses Elizabeth ve Edinburgh Dükü</i>
<i>Milletler Topluluğu gezisine çıktı.</i>

236
00:22:35.000 --> 00:22:38.360 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>19 saat sonra Kraliyet uçağı</i>
<i>Nairobi'ye iniş yaptı.</i>

237
00:22:38.440 --> 00:22:40.920 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Önlerinde 48 bin kilometrelik bir yol var</i>

238
00:22:41.000 --> 00:22:44.600 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>ve bu yolda beş ay içinde</i>
<i>üç kıtayı gezecekler.</i>

239
00:22:44.680 --> 00:22:48.240 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Bu yolculuğa aslında Kral çıkmak üzereydi</i>

240
00:22:48.320 --> 00:22:50.120 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>fakat hastalığı engel oldu.</i>

241
00:22:50.200 --> 00:22:53.160 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>Kraliyet çifti buradan</i>
<i>Sagana Lodge'a geçecek...</i>

242
00:23:24.320 --> 00:23:28.360 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Günaydın Majesteleri.
Saat 7:30 efendim.

243
00:23:32.640 --> 00:23:33.680 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Efendim?

244
00:24:05.960 --> 00:24:07.560 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Orada kal.

245
00:24:22.760 --> 00:24:26.760 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Üzülerek söylüyorum ki Kral vefat etti.

246
00:24:33.480 --> 00:24:36.640 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Hayır!

247
00:24:39.200 --> 00:24:40.240 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Lütfen!

248
00:25:41.120 --> 00:25:43.080 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Dışişleri Bakanı'nı arayın.

249
00:25:44.000 --> 00:25:45.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ona...

250
00:25:46.480 --> 00:25:50.600 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
...Hyde Park Corner deyin. Anlayacaktır.

251
00:25:56.520 --> 00:26:01.400 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Prenses'e haber verildi mi?
-Yeni Kraliçe'den mi bahsediyorsunuz?

252
00:26:01.480 --> 00:26:03.120 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Sanırım verilmedi.

253
00:26:03.200 --> 00:26:06.160 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Haberlere düşmeden versek iyi olur.

254
00:26:06.240 --> 00:26:10.600 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Deniyoruz. Tam olarak
nerede olduğundan emin değiliz.

255
00:26:10.680 --> 00:26:13.040 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Nairobi Valisi'ne ulaşmaya çalışıyoruz.

256
00:27:17.360 --> 00:27:18.360 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Gidelim!

257
00:27:24.400 --> 00:27:28.720 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>-Haberi vermeliyiz.</i>
-Yapamayız, onay gelmedi.

258
00:27:28.800 --> 00:27:30.960 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Sence dünyadaki diğer haberciler</i>

259
00:27:31.040 --> 00:27:33.120 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>onay gelmesini bekleyecek mi?</i>

260
00:27:33.200 --> 00:27:35.280 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
BBC ile tekrar konuştum.

261
00:27:35.360 --> 00:27:39.080 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Haber her yere yayılıyor.
Daha fazla bekleyemeyecekler.

262
00:27:39.160 --> 00:27:43.480 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Prenses'ten haber yok mu?
-Hayır. BBC için onay veriyor musunuz?

263
00:27:45.720 --> 00:27:46.720 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Veriyorum.

264
00:27:52.920 --> 00:27:54.240 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Tanrı onun yardımcısı olsun.

265
00:27:57.200 --> 00:27:58.880 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Sürekli motoru çalıştırmayı deniyorlar.

266
